
Passing :
|
- NOT on a curvy road
- NOT within 10 car lengths of a crossing
|
- dashed line + no oncoming traffic
- signal 10 car lengths in business/resid. areas
  - 30 car lengths on freeways/interstates 
- do not speed up
- move back when you can see the other vehicle in the rear-view mirror
|
When another vehicle wants to pass, move to the right.



PASSING PARKED VEHICLES - watch for :
- signals , lights
- movements
- anyone
- doors 

.